data.description: Are you looking for a MINI FARM conveniently located to the heart of Crossville? We have just the place for you! The property is partially fenced with new fencing and boasts a fully STOCKED POND as well as a barn, storage shed, chicken coop, and a goat pin! The perfect place for your animals to roam. Nestled on the quiet and UNRESTRICED 7.6 acres is a 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH 1332 SQ FT ranch house with light landscaping to create absolutely adorable curb appeal. The home features new gutters, new paint, and luxury vinyl plank flooring in the living room as well as tile through out the kitchen and laundry room. New laminate flooring was placed in the master bathroom as well. The cozy farmhouse kitchen comes fully equipped with all stainless steel appliances that are only a year old! The HVAC is 5 years old and the roof is only 3 years old!
